{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"regexp:replace()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/regexp/replace","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/exsl\">Common (exsl)</a><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/exsl\">Common (exsl)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/exsl/node-set\">exsl:node-set()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/exsl/object-type\">exsl:object-type()</a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/math\">Math (math)</a><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/math\">Math (math)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/math/highest\">math:highest()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/math/lowest\">math:lowest()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/math/max\">math:max()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/math/min\">math:min()</a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/regexp\">Regular expressions (regexp)</a><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/regexp\">Regular expressions (regexp)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/regexp/match\">regexp:match()</a></li><li><em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/regexp/replace\" aria-current=\"page\">regexp:replace()</a></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/regexp/test\">regexp:test()</a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/set\">Sets (set)</a><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/set\">Sets (set)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/set/difference\">set:difference()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/set/distinct\">set:distinct()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/set/has-same-node\">set:has-same-node()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/set/intersection\">set:intersection()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/set/leading\">set:leading()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/set/trailing\">set:trailing()</a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/str\">Strings (str)</a><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/str\">Strings (str)</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/str/concat\">str:concat()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/str/split\">str:split()</a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/str/tokenize\">str:tokenize()</a></li></ol></li></ol>\n","sidebarMacro":"QuickLinksWithSubpages","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath Reference</a></b>: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT elements</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT functions</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath functions</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath axes</a>\n</div>\n<p><code>regexp:replace()</code> replaces the portions of a string that match a given regular expression with the contents of another string.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">regexp:replace(originalString, regExpString, flagsString, replaceString)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"originalstring\"><a href=\"#originalstring\"><code>originalString</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The string perform a search-and-replace operation upon.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"regexpstring\"><a href=\"#regexpstring\"><code>regExpString</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The JavaScript style regular expression to evaluate.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"flagsstring\"><a href=\"#flagsstring\"><code>flagsString</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The string containing character flags.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"replacestring\"><a href=\"#replacestring\"><code>replaceString</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The string with which the matched substrings are to be replaced.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<p>The character flags are:</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"g\"><a href=\"#g\"><code>g</code></a> - Global replace</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>If this flag is specified, all occurrences of the regular expression within the <code>originalString</code> are replaced. Otherwise only the first occurrence is replaced.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"i\"><a href=\"#i\"><code>i</code></a> - Case insensitive match</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>If this flag is specified, the match is performed in a case insensitive fashion.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"Returns","isH3":true,"content":"<p>The revised version of the string.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://exslt.github.io/regexp/functions/replace/index.html\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">EXSLT - REGEXP:REPLACE</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"}],"summary":"regexp:replace() replaces the portions of a string that match a given regular expression with the contents of another string.","popularity":0,"modified":"2023-07-10T09:47:59.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/exslt/regexp/replace","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/exslt/regexp/replace/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/b6f343538eac4a803943b4e99b0c0545b372645a","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"regexp:replace()","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT","title":"EXSLT"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/regexp","title":"Regular expressions (regexp)"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT/regexp/replace","title":"regexp:replace()"}],"pageTitle":"regexp:replace() - EXSLT | MDN","noIndexing":false}}